    "text": "Let \\(n\\geq 5\\) be an integer. Show that \\(n ^ 2 > 2n + 11\\) . @[autograded 5] theorem problem1 { n : ℤ } ( hn : n ≥ 5 ) : n ^ 2 > 2 * n + 11 := sorry",
